message.content:
A black kitchen cabinet set spans an L-shaped corner. On its marble-look countertop, a sink is situated below a wooden-framed window, with a pot resting on a small stovetop to the right of the sink. Directly above the stove hangs a wooden-framed range hood. Near the stove, a yellow mug stands beside a box labeled “Chucky,” and a jar of jam sits next to it. Further along the countertop are boxes of Rice Bubbles cereal and Jell-O, as well as a second Chucky-labeled box, plates stacked one atop another, another jam jar, and a blue container of Alpen salt. Adjacent to these cabinets on the left is a tall black pantry, and continuing right from it stands a tall white refrigerator.

Beyond the refrigerator is an open dining area with a rectangular wooden table set over a parquet floor. Four white chairs, one on each side, surround the table. Centered on the tabletop is a white bowl containing several oranges and lemons. A large bottle of water stands upright inside that same bowl, and off to one side is a box of shortbread. A clear glass pitcher and a single wine glass sit nearby. A simple round ceiling light hangs above the table, and a white door is visible on the far wall behind one of the chairs.
